data.description: $16,000.00 Concession for Rate Buydown or other fees. New Paint, quiet street in back of subdivision, Private covered Patio that is shaded from the evening sun. Yard is Professionally landscaped. All windows have blinds. Newer Hot Water Heater and 220 outlet in Garage. Garage doors have openers installed. Many other upgrades have been made. If not represented with a buyer's agent Realtor, Please Call the Selling agent to schedule a time to show.  James @ 208-484-6365
